Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

python-gallery-dl (command-line program to download image galleries)

gallery-dl is a command-line program to download image galleries and
collections from several image hosting sites (see Supported Sites).
It is a cross-platform tool with many command-line and configuration
options, as well as powerful file-naming capabilities.

HOME: https://codeberg.org/mikf/gallery-dl

======================================================================
REQUIRES: mkvtoolnix python-pysocks python-secretstorage python-toml python-yt-dlp python-zstandard 

